{"data":[{"date":"14:24 23/06","title":"Wilshere r\u1eddi Arsenal, Mesut Ozil \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1edd ng\u00e0y n\u00e0y t\u1eeb r\u1ea5t l\u00e2u r\u1ed3i","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/23/wilshere-roi-arsenal-mesut-ozil-da-cho-ngay-nay-tu-rat-lau-roi.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Mesut Ozil mu\u1ed1n \u00e1o s\u1ed1 10 c\u1ee7a Jack Wilshere, nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng sau r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u n\u0103m c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tham v\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Jack Wilshere tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 r\u1eddi Arsenal</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nH\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Jack Wilshere v\u1edbi Arsenal c\u00f2n th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ebfn H\u00e8 2018, d\u00f9 \u0111\u00e3 nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n song hai b\u00ean v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 th\u00f4ng qua m\u1ed9t b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Mesut Ozil mu\u1ed1n \u00e1o s\u1ed1 10 c\u1ee7a Jack Wilshere h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Mesut Ozil mu\u1ed1n \u00e1o s\u1ed1 10 c\u1ee7a Jack Wilshere h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/20/Mesut-Ozil-muon-ao-so-10-cua-Jack-Wilshere-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Wilshere tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 chia tay Arsenal</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y kh\u00f4ng l\u00e2u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 cu\u1ed9c g\u1eb7p v\u1edbi HLV Emery \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u1ed1t t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai. \u00d4ng n\u00e0y kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi v\u1edbi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1992, song anh s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nVi\u1ec7c kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng y\u00eau c\u1ea7u ra s\u00e2n khi\u1ebfn Jack Wilshere ch\u00e1n n\u1ea3n, anh \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 ra \u0111i. <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/wilshere-chinh-thuc-roi-arsenal-172-188988.html\" target=\"_blank\">Wilshere r\u1eddi Arsenal </span>theo d\u1ea1ng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1ef1 do, Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng thu v\u1ec1 b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 xu n\u00e0o t\u1eeb th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHi\u1ec7n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 26 tu\u1ed5i \u0111ang \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 m\u1edbi, anh mu\u1ed1n ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh. Southampton, West Ham v\u00e0 Everton \u0111ang l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nD\u00f9 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1ecdng d\u1ee5ng \u1edf Arsenal nh\u01b0ng v\u1edbi kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh Wilshere \u0111\u1ee7 s\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng t\u1ea7m trung \u1edf gi\u1ea3i Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh. Ng\u00f4i sao 26 tu\u1ed5i \u0111ang r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n ch\u1ee9ng minh Emery \u0111\u00e3 sai khi kh\u00f4ng tr\u1ecdng d\u1ee5ng m\u00ecnh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Ozil vui nh\u1ea5t khi Wilshere r\u1eddi Arsenal</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1eeb khi Mesut Ozil c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Arsenal v\u00e0o n\u0103m 2013, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e3 mu\u1ed1n kho\u00e1c l\u00ean m\u00ecnh chi\u1ebfc \u00e1o s\u1ed1 10. Tuy nhi\u00ean, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 s\u1ed1 \u00e1o m\u00e0 Jack Wilshere \u0111\u00e3 \u0111eo t\u1eeb khi Robin van Persie chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi MU v\u00e0o n\u0103m 2012 v\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng l\u1ea1i cho tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Mesut Ozil muon khoac ao so 10\" title=\"Mesut Ozil mu\u1ed1n kho\u00e1c \u00e1o s\u1ed1 10\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/23/wilshere-roi-arsenal-mesut-ozil-da-cho-ngay-nay-tu-rat-lau-roi.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Mesut Ozil mu\u1ed1n kho\u00e1c \u00e1o s\u1ed1 10 do\u00a0Wilshere b\u1ecf l\u1ea1i</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nVi\u1ec7c kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 kho\u00e1c \u00e1o s\u1ed1 10 khi\u1ebfn Ozil ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ecdn s\u1ed1 11. C\u1ee9 m\u1ed7i m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i Ozil l\u1ea1i th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u01b0\u1edbc mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kho\u00e1c \u00e1o s\u1ed1 10 song \u00f4ng Wenger t\u00f4n tr\u1ecdng Jack Wilshere, b\u1edfi v\u1eady c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1988 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ee5c \u0111\u00edch c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTh\u1eadm ch\u00ed khi Wilshere ra \u0111i theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n th\u00ec s\u1ed1 10 \u1edf Arsenal v\u1eabn b\u1ecf tr\u1ed1ng, \u00f4ng Wenger t\u00f4n tr\u1ecdng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh d\u00f9 bi\u1ebft r\u1eb1ng Ozil kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nKhi m\u00e0 Wilshere \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c r\u1eddi Arsenal th\u00ec Ozil \u0111\u00e3 ngay l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c b\u00e0y t\u1ecf \u01b0\u1edbc mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kho\u00e1c \u00e1o s\u1ed1 10. Theo Daily Mail, Ozil \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eafn v\u1edbi HLV Emery r\u1eb1ng m\u00ecnh mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kho\u00e1c \u00e1o s\u1ed1 10 \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng mong mu\u1ed1n b\u1ea5y l\u00e2u c\u1ee7a Ozil s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, Ozil \u0111eo \u00e1o s\u1ed1 10 trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Real Madrid, \u0111\u00f3 c\u0169ng l\u00e0 s\u1ed1 \u00e1o m\u00e0 anh th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean kho\u00e1c l\u00ean m\u00ecnh \u1edf \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"499","checkdouble":"189348"},{"date":"14:38 23/06","title":"L\u1ed9 b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 m\u1edbi c\u1ee7a Mateo Kovacic","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/3/7/lo-ben-do-moi-cua-mateo-kovacic.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Tottenham mu\u1ed1n mua Mateo Kovacic c\u1ee7a Real Madrid, Spurs ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi t\u1edbi 35 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kovacic quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m r\u1eddi Real Madrid</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Mateo Kovacic kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Real Madrid. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Croatia ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 14 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh \u1edf hai m\u1eb7t tr\u1eadn ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 La Liga v\u00e0 Champions League.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Tottenham mu\u1ed1n mua Mateo Kovacic v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 35 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Tottenham mu\u1ed1n mua Mateo Kovacic v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 35 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/2/Tottenham-muon-mua-Mateo-Kovacic-voi-gia-35-trieu-bang-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>\u00a0Kovacic mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Real Madrid</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nVi\u1ec7c kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean khi\u1ebfn c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1994 ch\u00e1n n\u1ea3n, \u0111\u00edch th\u00e2n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ea7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201c\u1ede tu\u1ed5i 24, t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n. T\u00f4i c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng khi s\u1ed1 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf, t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n. N\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng y\u00eau c\u1ea7u t\u00f4i s\u1ebd quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh ra \u0111i\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTheo Marca, HLV Lopetegui s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng cho Kovacic m\u1ed9t v\u1ecb tr\u00ed ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi. \u00d4ng c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch t\u00ecm ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay th\u1ebf c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 24 tu\u1ed5i trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-tbn/kovacic-muon-roi-real-180-189338.html\" target=\"_blank\">Kovacic r\u1eddi Real Madrid</span>.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Tottenham ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 35 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua Kovacic</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tottenham mu\u1ed1n mua Mateo Kovacic c\u1ee7a Real Madrid, Spurs ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi t\u1edbi 35 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Tottenham mu\u1ed1n mua Mateo Kovacic v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 35 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"Tottenham mu\u1ed1n mua Mateo Kovacic v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 35 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/7/lo-ben-do-moi-cua-mateo-kovacic.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Tottenham mu\u1ed1n chi 35 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua Kovacic</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nHLV Pochettino s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng chia tay Dembele \u1edf H\u00e8 2018, hi\u1ec7n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c MU, AC Milan v\u00e0 PSG theo \u0111u\u1ed5i. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn b\u00e1n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1987 v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 30 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nS\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n b\u00e1n Dembele s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 Mateo Kovacic t\u1eeb Real Madrid. HLV Pochettino \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1994 v\u00e0 mu\u1ed1n BL\u0110 Spurs l\u00e0m m\u1ecdi c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y v\u1ec1 Tottenham.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nKovacic gia nh\u1eadp Real t\u1eeb Inter v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 22,5 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng H\u00e8 2015. L\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 35 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng c\u1ee7a Tottenham \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c Los Blancos nh\u1ea3 ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nN\u1ebfu Spurs \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y m\u1ed9t v\u1ecb tr\u00ed ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng h\u1ecd c\u00f3 \u0111i\u1ec1u m\u00ecnh c\u1ea7n l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t cao.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"498","checkdouble":"189349"},{"date":"14:38 23/06","title":"TR\u1ef0C TI\u1ebeP SLNA 1-0 C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1 (H2): Xu\u00e2n To\u00e0n m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/23/slna-vs-can-tho-vong-15-vleague-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp B\u1ec9 vs Tunisia: C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt li\u00ean t\u1ee5c di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u B\u1ec9 vs Tunisia b\u1ea3ng G World Cup 2018 l\u00fac 19h00 t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay 23/6.</h2><h2>Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp B\u1ec9 vs Tunisia: C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt li\u00ean t\u1ee5c di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u B\u1ec9 vs Tunisia b\u1ea3ng G World Cup 2018 l\u00fac 19h00 t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay 23/6.</h2>\r\n<br>\r\nB\u1ecb l\u1ed7i, vui l\u00f2ng click t\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/truc-tiep-world-cup-2018/tran-dau/link-xem-bi-vs-tunisia-463-189356.html\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(128, 0, 0);\"><strong>TR\u1ef0C TI\u1ebeP B\u1ec8 VS TUNISIA</strong></span></span><br>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"497","checkdouble":"189350"},{"date":"15:57 23/06","title":"\u0110\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i Brazil thanh minh cho th\u00f3i \u201cm\u00edt \u01b0\u1edbt\u201d c\u1ee7a Neymar","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/23/jesus-phat-bieu-ve-neymar-mit-uot-cua-dt-brazil.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Gabriel Jesus ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Neymar, \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u00ean tuy\u1ec3n Brazil. Anh kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 quan t\u00e2m t\u1edbi nh\u1eefng gi\u1ecdt n\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1eaft c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i sao PSG sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng Costa Rica.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Neymar l\u00e0 ch\u00e0ng trai vui v\u1ebb</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nBrazil m\u1edbi tr\u1ea3i qua tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7y kh\u00f3 nh\u1ecdc tr\u01b0\u1edbc Costa Rica. Ph\u1ea3i t\u1edbi ph\u00fat b\u00f9 gi\u1edd, h\u1ecd m\u1edbi ghi b\u00e0n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean t\u1edbi t\u1eeb c\u00fa d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1eadn th\u00e0nh c\u1ee7a Philippe Coutinho. V\u00e0i ph\u00fat sau, Neymar \u0111\u00f3ng l\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 2-0 cho Selecao trong s\u1ef1 sung s\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nSau ti\u1ebfng c\u00f2i m\u00e3n cu\u1ed9c, si\u00eau sao Neymar b\u1ed7ng d\u01b0ng g\u1ee5c xu\u1ed1ng s\u00e2n kh\u00f3c th\u00fat th\u00edt khi\u1ebfn ng\u01b0\u1eddi xem hoang mang. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, d\u01b0 lu\u1eadn s\u1ee3 r\u1eb1ng anh s\u1ebd t\u00e1i ph\u00e1t ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng b\u00e0n ch\u00e2n sau khi b\u1ecf d\u1edf m\u1ed9t bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp c\u1ee7a \u0110T Brazil.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Jesus ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Neymar, \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u00ean tuy\u1ec3n Brazil h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Jesus ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Neymar, \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u00ean tuy\u1ec3n Brazil h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/23/jesus-phat-bieu-ve-neymar-mit-uot-cua-dt-brazil.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Neymar b\u1eadt kh\u00f3c sau tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng Costa Rica</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTh\u00f4ng qua m\u1ea1ng x\u00e3 h\u1ed9i, Neymar chia s\u1ebb r\u1eb1ng anh c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y r\u1ea5t vui m\u1eebng v\u00ec s\u1ef1 h\u1ed3i ph\u1ee5c m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd sau ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng. V\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i Gabriel Jesus, anh tin r\u1eb1ng nh\u1eefng \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p c\u1ee7a Neymar c\u1ea7n nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 tr\u00e2n tr\u1ecdng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cNeymar \u1ed5n th\u00f4i. T\u00f4i l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ch\u00e0ng trai tr\u1ebb, anh \u1ea5y c\u0169ng v\u1eady, m\u1ed9t ch\u00e0ng trai vui v\u1ebb\u201d, Jesus ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Neymar. \u201cAnh \u1ea5y t\u1ecfa ra h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac cho t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 ch\u00fang ta, \u0111\u1ebfn c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ebfn Brazil. Kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 v\u00ec b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 c\u1ee7a Neymar m\u00e0 c\u00f2n l\u00e0 con ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u1ee7a anh \u1ea5y.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cCh\u00fang ta ph\u1ea3i tr\u00e2n tr\u1ecdng th\u1ea7n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. H\u00e3y tr\u00e2n qu\u00fd v\u00e0 tin v\u00e0o ni\u1ec1m tin \u0111\u00f3 cho \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eadn nh\u1eefng gi\u00e2y ph\u00fat cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Jesus mo ty so cho Brazil\" title=\"Jesus mo ty so cho Brazil\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/11/jesus-xem-nhe-danh-hieu-vua-pha-luoi-world-cup.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Jesus ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Neymar \u0111\u1ea7y t\u00edch c\u1ef1c</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>Jesus kh\u00f4ng s\u1ee3 Firmino</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nS\u1ef1 b\u00ecnh ph\u1ee5c c\u1ee7a Neymar gi\u00fap anh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o su\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018. Tuy nhi\u00ean, Jesus l\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c may m\u1eafn \u0111\u00f3. Anh lu\u00f4n trong t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng b\u1ecb so s\u00e1nh v\u1edbi Roberto Firmino v\u00e0 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 m\u1ea5t su\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 l\u00fac n\u00e0o.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, Jesus cho r\u1eb1ng th\u1eadt kh\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u00e1nh nh\u1eefng s\u1ef1 so s\u00e1nh v\u1edbi Firmino. \u201c\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u b\u00ecnh th\u01b0\u1eddng khi m\u00e0 hai c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ch\u01a1i cho \u0110TQG\u201d, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o 21 tu\u1ed5i n\u00f3i. \u201cQuy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh ai ra s\u00e2n thu\u1ed9c v\u1ec1 HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng Tite.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cNh\u01b0ng ph\u1ea3i n\u00f3i r\u1eb1ng c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 t\u00f4i, Firmino c\u00f3 t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t. Anh \u1ea5y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t. T\u00f4i hy v\u1ecdng r\u1eb1ng, d\u00f9 Firmino c\u00f3 ra s\u00e2n hay kh\u00f4ng, t\u00f4i v\u1eabn s\u1ebd ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 \u0110T Brazil tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/3-yeu-to-quyet-dinh-tran-dau-brazil-20-costa-rica-421-189317.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/22/3-yeu-to-quyet-dinh-tran-dau-brazil-20-costa-rica.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/3-yeu-to-quyet-dinh-tran-dau-brazil-20-costa-rica-421-189317.html\">4 y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Brazil 2-0 Costa Rica</span><br>\r\n<span>\u0110T Brazil cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u1ecdn v\u1eb9n tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1ed9t Costa Rica thi \u0111\u1ea5u ngoan c\u01b0\u1eddng v\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ee7ng l\u01b0\u1edbi \u1edf nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat cu\u1ed1i. V\u00e0 d\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 4 y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1...</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nhung-diem-nhan-brazil-vs-costa-rica-binh-luan-brazil-vs-costa-rica-421-189305.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/23/Coutinho-an-mung-sau-khi-ghi-ban-cho-Brazil.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nhung-diem-nhan-brazil-vs-costa-rica-binh-luan-brazil-vs-costa-rica-421-189305.html\">4 \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng ngh\u1eb9t th\u1edf c\u1ee7a Brazil tr\u01b0\u1edbc Costa Rica</span><br>\r\n<span>\u0110i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n Brazil vs Costa Rica kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 thi\u1ebfu s\u1ef1 t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng c\u1ee7a Coutinho v\u1edbi b\u00e0n khai th\u00f4ng b\u1ebf t\u1eafc t\u1eadn ph\u00fat b\u00f9 gi\u1edd. Tuy nhi\u00ean, \u0111\u00f3 c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u...</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"496","checkdouble":"189354"},{"date":"15:38 23/06","title":"TR\u1ef0C TI\u1ebeP H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i vs \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng 19h00 ng\u00e0y 23/6 (V-League 2018)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/23/ha-noi-vs-da-nang-vong-15-vleague-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i vs \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng: C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt li\u00ean t\u1ee5c di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i vs SHB \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng v\u00f2ng 15 gi\u1ea3i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch qu\u1ed1c gia V\u0110QG Vi\u1ec7t Nam V-League 2018 l\u00fac 19h00 t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay 23/6.</h2><h2>Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i vs \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng: C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt li\u00ean t\u1ee5c di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3